room_title: Escape room "Secrets of the Skunk Ape" by Rabbit Hole Escape Games in Tampa
room_description: In this adventure, you are students of a Cryptozoology Professor who has asked you to meet him at Cabbage Lake to discuss his latest findings. Upon arrival, however, you are greeted by the menacing rival team who stole the professor's notes, has locked you in his research trailer and are now out to hunt down the Skunk Ape. You must scramble to piece together the Professor's findings and get to the Skunk Ape before it's too late!
